The Alex Jones Show
Tuesday, 19 Mar 2013


[sebaygo1]


Show Description
................

From the Infowars web site :: On the Tuesday, March 19 edition of the Alex Jones Show, Alex breaks down the plan by the IMF and EU to steal billions from bank deposits in Cyprus as the global economy continues its slow-motion implosion. 

He also covers rising outrage over the Department of Homeland Security's massive and unprecedented ammo purchase and the Senate's plans to introduce legislation aimed squarely at the heart of the Second Amendment and the Bill of Rights. 

Alex welcomes back to the show activist and former presidential candidate Lyndon LaRouche and crypto-anarchist and law student Cody Wilson who developed and published open source gun designs suitable for 3D printing. Cody will join Alex in-studio.
